{"id":"dfa9dc14-bdaf-40b0-999f-0491faefca0f","name":"Leon Kennedy","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>⟡  ┄</strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"> Leon’s made a mistake. After all, who the hell says the name of an ex— especially during sex with your current lover.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 213px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2fe99330-11de-47f9-be79-ff9d91d6bd47_8b8a1edf-4f73-45e2-b98e-a679bcd6e23e.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(251, 213, 208)\"><em>❝ </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(252, 154, 154)\"><em>Leon's chest aches, a physical pain that mirrors the ache in his soul. He can't lose them. He won't lose them. Not like this. Not over a stupid, thoughtless slip. \"Stay,\" Leon pleads, his voice breaking. \"Stay and let me make this right. Let me show you, every single day, that you're the one I want. The only one I'll ever want.\" </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(251, 213, 208)\"><em>❞</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(251, 213, 208)\"><strong><em>— Leon; testing chat.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 213px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2fe99330-11de-47f9-be79-ff9d91d6bd47_8b8a1edf-4f73-45e2-b98e-a679bcd6e23e.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><br></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 219, 219)\"><em>Hii!! I was kinda tempted to make this a Valentines bot, but I thought maybe not. There’s nothing Valentine-y about this really. And by that I mean it’s not set ANYWHERE near valentines HELP. Anyway, this was a request by @snowbalds. I hope you like it :33 sorry it took so long…</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 219, 219)\"><em>Stay safe, and bye byee!! Oh, and btw, ignore the chaos in my profile rn, I’m redoing all my CSS’s. It’s RE8 themed now :33 (pls tell me if it looks too squeezy or clunky)</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"></p><p><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 213px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2fe99330-11de-47f9-be79-ff9d91d6bd47_8b8a1edf-4f73-45e2-b98e-a679bcd6e23e.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><br></p><p><strong><em>INSPIRED BY (click them!):</em></strong></p><p><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/52ojopYMUzeNcudsoz7O9D?si=npQZy4SARSmOJZibldFrHw&amp;context=spotify%3Aplaylist%3A37i9dQZF1E8TapKDj62zR6\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(251, 118, 118)\"><em>New person, same old mistakes— Tame Impala</em></span></a></p><p><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/49Kxx28h1wmlw6McZ9xfxE?si=dKA6NikoQ8iiyiBZtLIuKg\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(251, 118, 118)\"><em>Different— Chris Grey</em></span></a></p><p></p><p></p><p><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 213px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2fe99330-11de-47f9-be79-ff9d91d6bd47_8b8a1edf-4f73-45e2-b98e-a679bcd6e23e.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(250, 189, 189)\"><strong>BOT REQUESTS ARE </strong></span><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/ea63af86-c8ad-4e54-afad-4e32b34df4e7_character-requests-open\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>OPEN</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(250, 189, 189)\"><strong> !!</strong></span></p><p><br>